[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":339},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fhtml\u002F2022\u002F09\u002F24\u002Fthe-curious-button-type-attribute\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fhtml\u002F2022\u002F09\u002F24\u002Fthe-curious-button-type-attribute\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fhtml\u002F2022\u002F09\u002F24\u002Fthe-curious-button-type-attribute\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fhtml\u002F2022\u002F09\u002F24\u002Fthe-curious-button-type-attribute\u002F":315,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fhtml\u002F2022\u002F09\u002F24\u002Fthe-curious-button-type-attribute\u002F":324},"\u002Fhtml\u002F20220924\u002F1348879561\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":299,"date":300,"description":301,"extension":302,"lang":303,"meta":304,"navigation":305,"path":306,"readingMinutes":307,"seo":308,"standalone":309,"stem":310,"tags":311,"tldr":312,"updated":300,"url":313,"__hash__":314},"content\u002Fen\u002FHTML\u002Fthe-curious-button-type-attribute.md","The Curious Case of Button's `type` Attribute","9145270117",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":295},"minimark",[11,16,28,32,55,61,101,112,124,141,145,157,164,169,175,187,240,244,247,250,256,274,285,291],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19,23,24,27],"p",{},[20,21,22],"code",{},"button"," is a tag we use constantly, but it has some genuinely weird behaviour around its ",[20,25,26],{},"type"," attribute. Let me show you.",[12,29,31],{"id":30},"button-type","Button Type",[17,33,34,36,37,39,40,43,44,47,48,50,51,54],{},[20,35,22],{}," has three ",[20,38,26],{}," values: ",[20,41,42],{},"submit",", ",[20,45,46],{},"reset",", and ",[20,49,22],{},". Normally ",[20,52,53],{},"type=\"button\""," is just a plain button with no functionality. But real-world usage gets weird, which is what this post is about.",[17,56,57,58,60],{},"In practice we often use ",[20,59,22],{}," as a functional button:",[62,63,68],"pre",{"className":64,"code":65,"language":66,"meta":67,"style":67},"language-html shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\u003Cbutton type=\"button\">A button\u003C\u002Fbutton>\n","html","",[20,69,70],{"__ignoreMap":67},[71,72,75,79,82,86,89,93,96,98],"span",{"class":73,"line":74},"line",1,[71,76,78],{"class":77},"sMAXC","\u003C",[71,80,22],{"class":81},"sKpQp",[71,83,85],{"class":84},"sCcAr"," type",[71,87,88],{"class":77},"=",[71,90,92],{"class":91},"sTRMh","\"button\"",[71,94,95],{"class":77},">A button\u003C\u002F",[71,97,22],{"class":81},[71,99,100],{"class":77},">\n",[102,103,111],"iframe",{"height":104,"style":105,"scrolling":106,"title":107,"src":108,"frameBorder":106,"loading":109,"allowTransparency":110,"allowFullScreen":110},300,"width: 100%;","no","button - 1","https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fembed\u002FabGVoXJ?default-tab=html%2Cresult","lazy","true","\n  See the Pen \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fpen\u002FabGVoXJ\">\n  button - 1\u003C\u002Fa> by Ray (\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\">@hsiangfeng\u003C\u002Fa>)\n  on \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\">CodePen\u003C\u002Fa>.\n",[17,113,114,115,117,118,120,121,123],{},"Even without ",[20,116,53],{}," you get the same result, because ",[20,119,22],{},"'s default type is ",[20,122,22],{},":",[62,125,127],{"className":64,"code":126,"language":66,"meta":67,"style":67},"\u003Cbutton>A button\u003C\u002Fbutton>\n",[20,128,129],{"__ignoreMap":67},[71,130,131,133,135,137,139],{"class":73,"line":74},[71,132,78],{"class":77},[71,134,22],{"class":81},[71,136,95],{"class":77},[71,138,22],{"class":81},[71,140,100],{"class":77},[102,142,144],{"height":104,"style":105,"scrolling":106,"title":107,"src":143,"frameBorder":106,"loading":109,"allowTransparency":110,"allowFullScreen":110},"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fembed\u002FVwxrZgQ?default-tab=html%2Cresult","\n  See the Pen \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fpen\u002FVwxrZgQ\">\n  button - 1\u003C\u002Fa> by Ray (\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\">@hsiangfeng\u003C\u002Fa>)\n  on \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\">CodePen\u003C\u002Fa>.\n",[17,146,147,148,150,151,153,154,156],{},"I just said the default ",[20,149,26],{}," is ",[20,152,22],{},", but writing ",[20,155,26],{}," explicitly helps the browser parse the element faster.",[17,158,159],{},[160,161],"img",{"alt":162,"src":163},"no type","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FCK4WmVx.png",[17,165,166],{},[160,167],{"alt":22,"src":168},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FV31NESn.png",[17,170,171,172,174],{},"Writing ",[20,173,26],{}," also makes the button's purpose obvious to readers — and it dodges one specific gotcha.",[17,176,177,178,180,181,43,184,186],{},"What gotcha? If your ",[20,179,22],{}," lives inside a ",[20,182,183],{},"form",[20,185,26],{}," behaves unexpectedly. Quick example:",[62,188,190],{"className":64,"code":189,"language":66,"meta":67,"style":67},"\u003Cform action=\"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002F\" method=\"get\">\n  \u003Cbutton>A button\u003C\u002Fbutton>\n\u003C\u002Fform>\n",[20,191,192,216,230],{"__ignoreMap":67},[71,193,194,196,198,201,203,206,209,211,214],{"class":73,"line":74},[71,195,78],{"class":77},[71,197,183],{"class":81},[71,199,200],{"class":84}," action",[71,202,88],{"class":77},[71,204,205],{"class":91},"\"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002F\"",[71,207,208],{"class":84}," method",[71,210,88],{"class":77},[71,212,213],{"class":91},"\"get\"",[71,215,100],{"class":77},[71,217,219,222,224,226,228],{"class":73,"line":218},2,[71,220,221],{"class":77},"  \u003C",[71,223,22],{"class":81},[71,225,95],{"class":77},[71,227,22],{"class":81},[71,229,100],{"class":77},[71,231,233,236,238],{"class":73,"line":232},3,[71,234,235],{"class":77},"\u003C\u002F",[71,237,183],{"class":81},[71,239,100],{"class":77},[102,241,243],{"height":104,"style":105,"scrolling":106,"title":107,"src":242,"frameBorder":106,"loading":109,"allowTransparency":110,"allowFullScreen":110},"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fembed\u002FGRdOKaY?default-tab=html%2Cresult","\n  See the Pen \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fpen\u002FGRdOKaY\">\n  button - 1\u003C\u002Fa> by Ray (\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\">@hsiangfeng\u003C\u002Fa>)\n  on \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\">CodePen\u003C\u002Fa>.\n",[17,245,246],{},"Click \"A button\" and the page suddenly navigates. Weird, right?",[17,248,249],{},"You'd probably check the HTML to see what's wrong:",[17,251,252],{},[160,253],{"alt":254,"src":255},"Weird behaviour","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Ft6aEe7t.png",[17,257,258,259,261,262,264,265,267,268,270,271,273],{},"The HTML looks fine. So what's going on? Inside a ",[20,260,183],{},", the default ",[20,263,26],{}," of a ",[20,266,22],{}," switches from ",[20,269,22],{}," to ",[20,272,42],{},". That's why clicking it navigates the page.",[17,275,276,277,284],{},"On top of that, different browsers may have different defaults. See ",[278,279,283],"a",{"href":280,"rel":281},"https:\u002F\u002Fstackoverflow.com\u002Fquestions\u002F31644723\u002Fwhat-is-the-default-button-type",[282],"nofollow","this discussion"," for more details.",[17,286,287,288,290],{},"So in real-world dev, always write ",[20,289,26],{}," explicitly. Always.",[292,293,294],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-s